snippet.title: Counterpick Labs Steam Trailer
snippet.description:
Counterpick Labs is a cute, free-to-play platform fighter where players customize their character with quirky weapons and gadgets.
Wishlist now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2837280?utm_source=youtube
Play for free at https://www.counterpicklabs.com/
Join the Discord: https://discord.com/invite/z9jGz6f77H

By popular demand, Counterpick Labs is coming to Steam in 2024! See the FAQ for more: https://www.counterpicklabs.com/faq

Music: "Wow" by Steven O'Brien (steven-obrien.net)
